short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: VSCode Jumper is a chrome extension that allows you to open your GitHub repositories in VSCode.dev with just one click.

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
VSCode Jumper is a powerful chrome extension that streamlines your workflow by adding a button on GitHub repositories that opens the current repository in VSCode.dev with just one click. 
This extension is perfect for developers who frequently switch between their code and GitHub. No more copy-pasting URLs, or manually opening VSCode. With VSCode Jumper, you can easily access your code directly from GitHub and get back to coding in no time. Get your hands on VSCode Jumper today and take the first step towards a more efficient and productive workflow.
